description: The FTSE Australian Government Bond Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: AUD-denominated bonds issued by the Australian government Exposure across the whole yield curve (minimum time to maturity of 1 year) Minimum amount outstanding of AUD 750 million per bond Additional information on the Index and the general methodology behind the FTSE Russel indices can be found on FTSE Russel Index website ( https://www.yieldbook.com/ ).
name: Xtrackers II Australia Government Bond UCITS ETF 1C
